nodes.text: Star Wars Bust Collection 3 is the third issue of the Star Wars Bust Collection magazine published by Fanhome. Subscribers received it, along with a bust of Chewbacca, with their second shipment of busts in 2021.

The magazine incorrectly states that Jedi Master Luminara Unduli was killed by her clone troopers during Order 66, despite it being established in "Rise of the Old Masters" that she survived and was imprisoned on Stygeon Prime.
